ion, and accessible item actions — built on RAC GridList.</p><div class=\"mb-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><a class=\"button button--tertiary relative gap-2 dark:bg-default/70 button--sm\" href=\"https://storybook.heroui.pro/?path=/docs/components-listview--docs\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" fill=\"none\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"1em\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" width=\"1em\" class=\"text-lg text-[#ff4785]\"><g><path d=\"M356.5,5.2L353.9,63c-0.1,3.2,3.7,5.2,6.3,3.2l22.6-17.1L401.9,64c2.5,1.7,5.8,0,6-3l-2.2-58.8l28.4-2.2   c14.7-1,27.3,10.8,27.3,25.6v460.8c0,14.7-12.3,26.3-26.9,25.6L91.1,496.6c-13.3-0.6-24.1-11.3-24.5-24.7l-16-422.3   c-0.8-14.2,9.9-26.3,24.1-27.1L356.2,4.7L356.5,5.2z M291,198.4c0,10,67.4,5.1,76.6-1.7c0-68.2-36.7-104.3-103.6-104.3   c-67.2,0-104.5,36.8-104.5,91.6c0,94.9,128,96.6,128,148.4c0,15-6.8,23.5-22.4,23.5c-20.5,0-28.8-10.4-27.7-46.1   c0-7.7-77.8-10.3-80.4,0c-5.7,86,47.6,110.9,108.7,110.9c59.6,0,106.1-31.7,106.1-89.1c0-101.7-130.1-99-130.1-149.3   c0-20.7,15.4-23.4,24.1-23.4c9.7,0,26.7,1.5,25.4,39.8L291,198.4z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></g></svg>Storybook</a></div></section><div class=\"prose flex-1 prose-sm\"><h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"usage\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#usage\" class=\"peer\">Usage</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>The <code>ListView</code> component displays a list of interactive items with built-in keyboard navigation, typeahead search, and selection.</p>\n"}, {"type": "demo", "slug": "list-view-default"}, {"type": "html", "html": "\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"selection-modes\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#selection-modes\" class=\"peer\">Selection Modes</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>ListView supports three selection modes: <code>none</code> (read-only), <code>single</code> (radio-style), and <code>multiple</code> (checkboxes). Selection checkboxes are rendered automatically when selection is enabled.</p>\n"}, {"type": "demo", "slug": "list-view-selection-modes"}, {"type": "html", "html": "\n<figure dir=\"ltr\" class=\"my-4 bg-fd-card rounded-xl shiki relative border shadow-sm not-prose overflow-hidden text-sm mdx-code-block shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark\" style=\"--shiki-light:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#e1e4e8;--shiki-light-bg:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#24292e\" tabindex=\"-1\"><div class=\"z-1! empty:hidden absolute top-3 right-2 z-2 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-lg text-fd-muted-foreground\"><button aria-label=\"Copy Text\" type=\"button\" class=\"button button--icon-only button--sm button--ghost text-muted -mt-0.5 bg-transparent\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"1em\" role=\"img\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"1em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12 2.5H8A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 6.5 4v1H8a3 3 0 0 1 3 3v1.5h1A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 13.5 8V4A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 12 2.5M11 11h1a3 3 0 0 0 3-3V4a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H8a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v1H4a3 